The following scripts require /etc/ncid/ncidscript.conf to be edited

Script to keep lines in logfile, on Linux, after it is rotated:
    cidrotate

Script to send CID to a pager or cell phone:
    IMPORTANT: sendmail.cf must hide user root when masquerading is used.
    ncid-page

Script to send CID to samba to get a popup:
    ncid-samba

Script to send CID to a text-to-speach program:
    ncid-speak
